We have the following mailinglists for debian-backports:

* [Backports](http://lists.debian.org/debian-backports-users) - For bugreporting and discussions about debian-backports 
* [Backports Announce](http://lists.debian.org/debian-backports-announce) - (Security) Announces for backports.org
* [Backports Changes](http://lists.debian.org/debian-backports-queue) - Messages from the backports queued and the Repository (DAK)
